### 1. Register a new user (✅ 정상 등록)
POST http://localhost:3000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 2. Register with the same email again (❌ 중복 사용자 등록)
POST http://localhost:3000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "anotherPassword"
}

### 3. Register with missing fields (❌ 입력값 부족)
POST http://localhost:3000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### 4. Login with correct credentials (✅ 정상 로그인 - 토큰 필요)
POST http://localhost:3000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 5. Login with wrong password (❌ 비밀번호 틀림)
POST http://localhost:3000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "wrongPassword"
}

### 6. Login with non-existent user (❌ 존재하지 않는 사용자)
POST http://localhost:3000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "noone@example.com",
  "password": "anything"
}

### 7. Send chat message with valid token (✅ 인증된 메시지 전송)
# Replace <VALID_TOKEN> with token from step 4
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6InVzZXJAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NTA0NDAzODksImV4cCI6MTc1MDQ0Mzk4OX0.nT4N4JYaz4dsKZhNxINNcAXMl0TKpKGvsNAgKqxt_hE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello, this is a secure message!"
}

### 8. Send chat message without token (❌ 인증 없이 메시지 전송)
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This should not be accepted"
}

### 9. Send chat message with forged JWT (❌ 위조 토큰 사용)
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6Imh1Y2tlckBleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsImlhdCI6MTYwMDAwMDAwMCwiZXhwIjoyNjAwMDAwMDAwfQ.signature_removed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a forged token message"
}

### 10. Get chat history with valid token (✅ 인증된 사용자만 가능)
# Replace <VALID_TOKEN> with token from step 4
GET http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6InVzZXJAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NTA0NDAzODksImV4cCI6MTc1MDQ0Mzk4OX0.nT4N4JYaz4dsKZhNxINNcAXMl0TKpKGvsNAgKqxt_hE

### 11. Get chat history without token (❌ 인증 없이 접근)
GET http://localhost:3000/chat

### 12. Get chat history with expired or invalid token (❌ 유효하지 않은 토큰)
GET http://localhost:3000/chat
Authorization: Bearer invalid.jwt.token
